instructions:
The following skills are named for use by macros. The skill value is stored as the attributes `max`, while the user-defined name is stored as the attribute's `current`.

* @{general-athletics}
* @{struggle}
* @{dodge}
* @{gallop}
* @{initiative}
* @{ponykinesis}
* @{flight}
* @{weather-control}
* @{basic-education}
* @{notice}
* @{hide}
* @{alchemy}
* @{unicorn-magic}
* @{charm}
* @{lie}
* @{shapeshifting}
* @{water-control}

Other skills are named @{_attribute_-skill-_number_}, for example @{soul-skill-6}. The number is based on the position in the list, so for example there is no body-skill-1 or body-skill-2, as those positions are taken by general-athletics and struggle.
